sajna de bajo mai te ji k hud ki krna rabba
anjubi hun muk gaye sare hurte mila de rabba


kismat ka ye khel hai milna tha humne kabhi
haatho ki lakiro me likha tha ye sabhi
koi jane na maane ye sath hai kitna hansi
kash yea pal tham jaye aapke hum ban jaye
jannat bhula k hum teri aankho k ashq ban jaye
kash yea pal tham jaye aapke hum ban jaye
jannat bhula k hum teri aankho k ashq ban jaye...


janam janma ka ye sath hai chhuta ye aise nahi
pyar tera aisa mila ki ab koi bhata nahi
baaho me aake teri saanso me simat jaye
kash yea pal tham jaye aapke hum ban jaye
jannat bhula k hum teri aankho k ashq ban jaye
kash yea pal tha jaye aapke hum ban jaye
jannat bhula k hum teri aankho k ashq ban jaye...


ashq ban jaye ye pal tham jaye
ashq ban jaye ye pal tham jaye
ashq ban jaye ye pal tham jaye
ashq ban jaye ye pal tham jaye
haatho ki kismat ka koi jane na mane 
ye sath hai kitna hansi 
kash ye.. 
aapke hum..
jannat bhula k hum teri aankho k ashq ban jaye
kash yea pal tham jaye aapke hum ban jaye
jannat bhula k hum teri aankho k ashq ban jaye
